          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "With major climate cases pending before the high court, Barrett was asked by Republican Sen. John Kennedy if she had thought about climate change. She responded: “I’ve read about climate change. I’m certainly not a scientist. I mean, I’ve read things on climate change. I would not say I have firm views on it.”",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
